{"type": "article", "id": 30798, "title": "解谜书", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-09T23:01:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160809181355XBF2MNrZ1Lu0a6Av.png", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>如果你热衷于动手解谜，这本名为 <a href=\"http://bw23brady.wix.com/portfolio#!codex-silenda-project/t9jub\" rel=\"nofollow\">Codex Silenda</a> 的解谜书会让你眼前一亮。它包含了五页不同的谜题，只有解开之后才可以翻至下一页，增强了可玩性。设计师还在书中穿插了达芬奇一位学徒的故事，其中的线索也与谜题息息相关。精妙的机械结构以及神秘的文字使它看起来就像是一件艺术品，放在桌上用作装饰也是一个不错的选择。Codex Silenda 在 Kickstarter 上线后仅用了六个小时就筹到了目标资金，制作团队会在第一批 400 本制作完成之后再开放额外的名额。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2119414279/codex-silenda-the-book-of-puzzles\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹页面</a>中的链接进行预约。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809181411dRk6gmrC5KI3ljx9.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809181411Nc3GY1xTAFLfBzDg.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809181411cjzgpfiSAOLTkdI9.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809181412jsXxFgaYdE720zMq.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}